sequenceDiagram
    actor Guard as Security Guard
    actor Admin as System Administrator
    participant UI as JavaFX Screens
    participant Service as PendingRegistrationService
    participant DAO as StudentDAO / DeviceDAO
    participant DB as Relational Database
    participant Audit as AuditService

    Guard->>UI: Submit pending student/device details with proof if student is not encoded
    UI->>Service: submitPendingRegistration(details, guard)
    Service->>Service: Validate minimum details, proof fields, and duplicates
    Service->>DAO: Save pending student/device
    DAO->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE pending records
    Service->>Audit: record pending submission
    Service-->>UI: Pending saved
    Admin->>UI: Open pending approval list
    UI->>Service: reviewPending()
    Service->>DAO: Load pending records
    DAO->>DB: SELECT pending records
    DB-->>DAO: Pending list
    DAO-->>Service: Pending list
    Admin->>UI: Review proof, then approve or reject
    UI->>Service: decidePending(id, decision, reason)
    Service->>DAO: Update registration_status and reviewer fields
    DAO->>DB: UPDATE pending record
    Service->>Audit: record approval/rejection
